description:
The purpose of this app is for three main reasons: 1) It is designed to be a sample application to allow new and current clients see the opportunities for app development and placement, 2) Provide contact information for our company, 3) Offer a discount coupon for your next web or mobile app project. 

North Bay Networking has been providing Website Design, Database Design, Computer Repair and IT Consulting for over 10 years to the San Francisco, Sonoma, and Napa counties. We can custom design anything you can think of from shopping carts to private portals to full web based communities and of course are now in the Mobile App business. Please contact us any time if you would like to learn more about our how we can serve you. We would love to set up a time to meet with you and go over any questions you may have – no charge.
